extends ./layout.pug

append head
  title Herp Project

  meta(name='title' content='Herp Project')
  meta(name='description' content='Herp Project strives to make the best products it can, we only want to make products that can help people and innovate the experience.')

  meta(property='og:type' content='website')
  meta(property='og:url' content='https://herpproject.com')
  meta(property='og:title' content='Herp Project')
  meta(property='og:description' content='Herp Project (HPJ) is an Egyptian technology company.')
  meta(property='og:image' content='https://herpproject.com/card.png')

  link(rel='stylesheet' href='../styles/body.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='../styles/icons.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='../styles/projects.css')

append content
  .projects.container

    .project.container
      .project.circle
        +icon('kbf-icon')
      .project.card
        a(href='https://bedan.me') Kuruit Bedan Fash5
      .project.info
        p A fill-in-the-blank party game where all the cards are made by the community.

    hr.project.separator
    .project.container
      .project.circle
        +icon('abram-icon')
      .project.card
        p Abram
      .project.info
        p Currently under development
        br
        //- p Abram is an app that allows you to forge new friendships, it was designed with the principles of psychology and a focus on mental health, it suggests new friends for you based on a lot of different things, and then encourages you to talk to them. the HPJ team wants you to know that they have a lot of ambitions, passion, hope, and love for Abram.

    hr.project.separator
    .project.container
      .project.circle
        +icon('question-mark')
      .project.card
        p Fabric
      .project.info
        p Due to the shift in the company's core focus, this project is not prioritized and is not in active development.
        br
        p Fabric is a high-performance vector graphics drawing library, built to push the limits of today's 2-d video games and 2-d animations by rendering them in real-time vector graphics.

    hr.project.separator
    .project.container
      .project.circle
        +icon('dawayer-icon')
      .project.card
        a(href='https://gitlab.com/hpj/Dawayer') Dawayer
      .project.info
        p Dawayer is discontinued.
        br
        p Dawayer is an audio player built with web technologies it lets you play local files, download and stream podcasts, stream music from a streaming service, Dawayer also has a feed page that gives you personalized playlists, statistics about your listening habits and notifies you when your favorite artist published a new track or a new podcast episode.

    hr.project.separator
    .project.container
      .project.circle
        +icon('sulaiman-icon')
      .project.card
        a(href='https://gitlab.com/hpj/Sulaiman') Sulaiman
      .project.info
        p Sulaiman is discontinued.
        br
        p Sulaiman is an expendable keyboard launcher built with powerful API for extensions, each extension runs on its separate sandbox, Sulaiman also comes with a set of useful built-in extension and a set of basic features and options to help you use it comfortably.

    hr.project.separator
    .project.container
      .project.circle
        +icon('question-mark')
      .project.card
        p Safehaven
      .project.info
        p To be announced
